<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12092d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12092d">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12092d"> 92(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> S.P asks to be 13<sup>th</sup> judge</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">All the disciples except Thomas now arrived on clouds, and greeted her. They were John, James his brother, Peter, Paul, Andrew, Philip, Luke, Barnabas, Bartholomew, Matthew, Matthias surnamed Justus, Simon the Canaanite, Jude and his brother, Nicodemus, Maximianus (this must be the legendary Maximin of Aix en Provence who figures in the late legend of Mary Magdalene&apos;s mission to Marseilles). <small> Montague Rhodes James, <a name="APNT" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#APNT"><cite title="source">The Apocryphal New Testament</cite></a> (1924) 217</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
